						               													<description>Shootout in Silver Creek is an entertaining and fast-paced dice and card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Take a trip back to the old days of The Wild West and try your hand at running the town of SILVER CREEK. The fight for Silver Creek ain't fer yer average cowpoke. You and your gang are not alone in eyeing the possibilities of the town. So now, the down and the dirty fight has begun in earnest, where all bets are off!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game offers many opportunities to be a real outlaw: fighting, brawling, shooting, robbery and hanging are a small part of what your gang has to go through to claim the prize that is Silver Creek.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You are divided into two bands of outlaws, fighting each other using cards played each turn. On your turn, you can play both a single Instant Card and a single Shooting Card. The Instant Cards offer a variety of special effects, while the Shooting Cards allows you to roll the dice and see if you wound your target! Every outlaw begins the game at 10 health, and if you ever run out you're out of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When there is only one gang left standing, they gain control of Silver Creek and win the game. Good luck cowboy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
